Stage 1: Basic Ore and Ingot Price Fetcher (Dynamis DC)

Objective:
Create a Python script that fetches the current market prices of ores and ingots on Dynamis (including Halicarnassus), and posts a summary to Discord via a bot.





Step 1: Fetch Prices from Universalis

Use their API to get item prices:

Endpoint:

https://universalis.app/api/v2/data-center/Dynamis/{item_ids}






Step 2: Define a Small Item List to Start With

- going to seperate the ores and ingots into two files
ores.txt
ingots.txt


Step 3: Fetch & Display Price Info




Step 4: Add Basic Discord Bot Integration
